y the increased popularity of long-haul flights to and from Hong Kong in the first half of the month, among students and those visiting friends and relatives.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lavinia\", \"score\": 0.9999999978255119, \"rank\": 1.9951844080104616e-09, \"text\": \"Lavinia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lavinia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lavinia\"}, {\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\", \"score\": 0.9876478528265241, \"rank\": 0.012499742145838941, \"text\": \"Lau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.213285289045566e-15, \"text\": \"Cathay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9976776577713313, \"rank\": 0.001062069926828201, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In addition, we saw strong demand for flights to Paris due to the Olympic Games, and we were delighted to carry a significant number of athletes and spectators to attend this momentous sporting occasion,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999973091425823, \"rank\": 2.690864597327566e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lau also highlighted the increase in travel to popular short-haul destinations in Japan and Southeast Asia during the latter half of July.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\", \"score\": 0.9876478528265241, \"rank\": 0.012499742145838941, \"text\": \"Lau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\"}, {\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.6785023590238262, \"rank\": 0.465655697871305, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In total, Cathay carried 12,667,826 passengers in the first seven months of this year, a 32.5 per cent increase compared with the same period in 2023.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.213285289045566e-15, \"text\": \"Cathay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\"}]}]}"